<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥ - السهو في رسم بعض الكلمات.<span style="color:#006d98"> ومن أمثلة ذلك:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كتابة <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كلما»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كل ما»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عمر»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عمرو»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«محفوضة»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«محفوظة»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إلا»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٤)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إلى»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ظامر»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٥)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضامر»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أضلله»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٦)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أظلله»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«همزت»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٧)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«همزة»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">ومما جاء من ذلك في المخطوطة الثانية:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>كتابة <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عمر»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٨)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عمرو»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98"> و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ويجرى»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٩)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«زمخشري»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مخفوظا»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٠)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مخفوضا»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مخفوظها»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١١)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مخفوضها»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«خفظا»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٢)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«خفضا»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ظابطهما»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٣)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضابطهما»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مخفوظين»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٤)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مخفوضين»</span>،<span style="color:#006d98">و:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«يحفض»</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٥)</span> بدل <span style="color:#6c6c00">«يحفظ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٦ - الاحتجاج ببعض ما في الكتب مع وجود خلاف فيه بين نسخها. ومن<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
